d to evacuate after wildfire crosses border from Washington state. Firefighters are using water cannon from planes to try to control the blaze, which is estimated to be 885 hectares (2,200 acres) in size. Local authorities estimate the blaze is 885-heater-size.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Mon, 31 Jul 2023 08:44:36 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">world</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/video/2023/jul/31/wildfires-cross-us-border-into-canada-triggering-evacuation-order-video" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/education/video/2023/jul/28/how-i-survived-a-sex-ed-shitstorm-video" target="_blank">How I survived a 'sex-ed shitstorm' – video - The Guardian</a></h2><div class="description"> Cartoonist Fiona Katauskas's book, The Amazing True Story of How Babies are Made, had been on Kmart and Big W shelves for three years. What started as a debate over the offending picture on Facebook would explode over several days into multiple headlines. Here is her take on what happened.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Thu, 27 Jul 2023 15:00:43 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">world</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/education/video/2023/jul/28/how-i-survived-a-sex-ed-shitstorm-video" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/video/2023/jul/26/sinead-oconnor-the-turbulent-career-of-the-irish-sensation-video-obituary" target="_blank">The life and career of Sinéad O’Connor: ‘I was really a protest singer’ - video obituary - The Guardian</a></h2><div class="description"> Sinéad O'Connor has died at the age of 56, prompting grief and tributes. Iri